52:03.400 --> 52:06.360
Tell you what, though, we
haven't half had some laughs.

52:06.400 --> 52:08.520
-We have.
-(LAUGHTER)

52:08.560 --> 52:11.480
-It was brilliant, wasn't it?
-Yeah, it's all
just brilliant.

