52:45.160 --> 52:48.000
-(LAUGHTER)
-You'd burst into laughter
straight away,

52:48.040 --> 52:49.920
"Ha-ha! He's hurt himself!"

52:49.960 --> 52:53.800
A whole 17 years of
your mates not giving a shit.

52:53.840 --> 52:55.040
(LAUGHTER)

