We do have some good news,
we're not.

54:04.480 --> 54:06.000
-No.
-(CHEERING)

54:06.040 --> 54:09.120
-We're not stopping.
-We can't.
We'd have to get jobs.

54:09.160 --> 54:10.720
Eugh!

54:10.760 --> 54:12.360
No, we're not
actually stopping.

54:12.400 --> 54:15.920
I mean the truth is, Amazon
loves us, we love Amazon.

54:15.960 --> 54:18.480
So we'll carry on a bit,
yeah?

