Thing is, there is...

54:40.800 --> 54:43.520
-That's uh...
-There is...

54:43.560 --> 54:45.280
Thank you.

54:45.320 --> 54:48.040
There's still so much of the
world we haven't been to yet.

54:48.080 --> 54:50.760
So many people
I haven't insulted.

54:50.800 --> 54:53.080
There are so many cars
he hasn't crashed.

54:53.120 --> 54:58.520
-There's a few.
-Exactly. So although this is
gone, The Grand Tour goes on.

54:58.560 --> 55:00.360
-(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)
-It goes on!

55:00.400 --> 55:02.440
It goes on.

55:02.480 --> 55:05.080
We are gonna need
walking sticks and nappies.

55:05.120 --> 55:07.280
-No, we are.
